audio_pic":"","status":"0","content":"","type":"2","content_zh":"","audio_time_human":"0","parentPath":"","title":"954d46de808800b729248ad0469ee89d","formatType":"mp3","filePath":"https:\/\/img.kmf.com\/ielts\/listening\/audio\/954d46de808800b729248ad0469ee89d.mp3","picPath":"","html_content":"","section_type":"0"}],"lyric":{"24043":{"id":"124210","content":"","content_zh":"","words_num":"0","level":"0","parent":"0","seq":"0","start_time":"","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"244.00","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"","section":[{"id":"124211","content":"","content_zh":"","words_num":"1186","level":"1","parent":"124210","seq":"1","start_time":"00:01.20","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"243.00","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","sentence":[{"id":"124212","content":"CAROL: It\u2019s really good to see you, Tom. Since I had to give up work, I feel I\u2019m losing touch with my friends and colleagues.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u771f\u9ad8\u5174\u89c1\u5230\u4f60\uff0c\u6c64\u59c6\u3002\u81ea\u4ece\u6211\u4e0d\u5f97\u4e0d\u8f9e\u53bb\u5de5\u4f5c\u4ee5\u6765\uff0c\u611f\u89c9\u548c\u670b\u53cb\u3001\u540c\u4e8b\u4e4b\u95f4\u7684\u8054\u7cfb\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u5c11\u4e86\u3002","words_num":"25","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"1","start_time":"00:01.20","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"7.36","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"1.20"},{"id":"124213","content":"TOM: We really miss you in the office \u2013 we were all so sorry you had to leave. But you must be relieved to have more time to look after your mother. How is she?","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u6211\u4eec\u90fd\u7279\u522b\u6000\u5ff5\u4f60\u5728\u529e\u516c\u5ba4\u7684\u65e5\u5b50\u2014\u2014\u5927\u5bb6\u5bf9\u4f60\u79bb\u5f00\u90fd\u633a\u9057\u61be\u7684\u3002\u4e0d\u8fc7\u4f60\u73b0\u5728\u6709\u66f4\u591a\u65f6\u95f4\u7167\u987e\u5988\u5988\uff0c\u5e94\u8be5\u4e5f\u8f7b\u677e\u4e86\u4e0d\u5c11\u5427\uff1f\u5979\u6700\u8fd1\u600e\u4e48\u6837\uff1f","words_num":"35","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"2","start_time":"00:08.56","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"9.28","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"8.56"},{"id":"124214","content":"CAROL: Well, she\u2019s very cheerful but she needs a lot of help.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u55ef\uff0c\u5979\u633a\u4e50\u89c2\u7684\uff0c\u4f46\u786e\u5b9e\u9700\u8981\u6211\u7ecf\u5e38\u7167\u987e\u3002","words_num":"12","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"3","start_time":"00:17.84","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"4.04","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"17.84"},{"id":"124215","content":"TOM: Have you tried to get any support from the local council?","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u4f60\u6709\u6ca1\u6709\u8bd5\u7740\u5411\u5f53\u5730\u653f\u5e9c\u7533\u8bf7\u4e00\u4e9b\u5e2e\u52a9\uff1f","words_num":"12","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"4","start_time":"00:21.88","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"3.00","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"21.88"},{"id":"124216","content":"CAROL: No. I didn\u2019t know I could.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u6ca1\u6709\uff0c\u6211\u8fd8\u771f\u4e0d\u77e5\u9053\u53ef\u4ee5\u8fd9\u4e48\u505a\u3002","words_num":"7","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"5","start_time":"00:24.88","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"2.60","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"24.88"},{"id":"124217","content":"TOM: Yes, they offer different kinds of practical support. They realise that carers sometimes need time for all the other responsibilities they have apart from the person they\u2019re caring for, and also that they sometimes need a break.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u5176\u5b9e\u4ed6\u4eec\u63d0\u4f9b\u5f88\u591a\u5b9e\u9645\u7684\u5e2e\u52a9\u3002\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u77e5\u9053\uff0c\u7167\u987e\u522b\u4eba\u7684\u540c\u65f6\uff0c\u4f60\u4e5f\u9700\u8981\u7a7a\u51fa\u65f6\u95f4\u5904\u7406\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u53ea\u662f\u4f11\u606f\u4e00\u4e0b\u3002","words_num":"38","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"6","start_time":"00:27.48","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"13.08","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"27.48"},{"id":"124218","content":"CAROL: Absolutely. OK, so tell me more. How do I go about getting this support?","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u8bf4\u5f97\u5bf9\u3002\u90a3\u4f60\u80fd\u8be6\u7ec6\u8bf4\u8bf4\u5417\uff1f\u6211\u8981\u600e\u4e48\u505a\u624d\u80fd\u5f97\u5230\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5e2e\u52a9\uff1f","words_num":"15","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"7","start_time":"00:40.56","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"8.20","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"40.56"},{"id":"124219","content":"TOM: Well, you\u2019d have to have an assessment of your mother\u2019s needs.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u9996\u5148\uff0c\u4f60\u9700\u8981\u4e3a\u4f60\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u9700\u6c42\u505a\u4e00\u4e2a\u8bc4\u4f30\u3002","words_num":"12","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"8","start_time":"00:48.76","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"3.24","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"48.76"},{"id":"124220","content":"TOM: That means someone would come round and talk to you about the situation and what you need.","content_zh":"\u5c31\u662f\u8bf4\u4f1a\u6709\u4eba\u4e0a\u95e8\u4e86\u89e3\u4f60\u4eec\u7684\u60c5\u51b5\uff0c\u770b\u770b\u4f60\u9700\u8981\u54ea\u4e9b\u5e2e\u52a9\u3002","words_num":"18","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"9","start_time":"00:52.00","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"4.56","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"52.00"},{"id":"124221","content":"TOM: So for a start they\u2019d want to know the amount of time you spend looking after your mother every day.","content_zh":"\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u5148\u4e86\u89e3\u4f60\u6bcf\u5929\u82b1\u591a\u5c11\u65f6\u95f4\u7167\u987e\u4f60\u6bcd\u4eb2\u3002","words_num":"21","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"10","start_time":"00:56.56","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"4.76","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"56.56"},{"id":"124222","content":"CAROL: OK.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u597d\u7684\u3002","words_num":"2","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"11","start_time":"01:01.32","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"1.00","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"61.32"},{"id":"124223","content":"TOM: Then they\u2019ll probably ask you what sorts of tasks you do for your mother during the day. Things like if she needs help with getting dressed, for example.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u7136\u540e\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u80fd\u8fd8\u4f1a\u95ee\u4f60\u5e73\u65f6\u90fd\u5e2e\u5988\u5988\u505a\u4e9b\u4ec0\u4e48\uff0c\u6bd4\u5982\u5979\u662f\u5426\u9700\u8981\u4eba\u5e2e\u5fd9\u7a7f\u8863\u670d\u4e4b\u7c7b\u7684\u3002","words_num":"29","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"12","start_time":"01:02.32","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"7.96","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"62.32"},{"id":"124224","content":"CAROL: Right. I help her with that, and also I help her get into the shower in the morning.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u662f\u7684\uff0c\u6211\u6bcf\u5929\u65e9\u4e0a\u90fd\u8981\u5e2e\u5979\u7a7f\u8863\uff0c\u8fd8\u8981\u5e2e\u5979\u6d17\u6fa1\u3002","words_num":"19","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"13","start_time":"01:10.28","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"5.80","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"70.28"},{"id":"124225","content":"TOM: Yes, that sort of thing. They\u2019ll probably ask you if you do the shopping for her, and help her at mealtimes. And whether she can cope using money.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u5bf9\uff0c\u5c31\u662f\u8fd9\u4e9b\u65b9\u9762\u3002\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u80fd\u8fd8\u4f1a\u95ee\u4f60\u6709\u6ca1\u6709\u5e2e\u5979\u4e70\u4e1c\u897f\u3001\u505a\u996d\uff0c\u8fd8\u6709\u5979\u4f1a\u4e0d\u4f1a\u81ea\u5df1\u7ba1\u7406\u94b1\u3002","words_num":"29","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"14","start_time":"01:16.08","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"9.08","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"76.08"},{"id":"124226","content":"CAROL: Yes, that\u2019s becoming a bit of a problem. She used to be very good at it, but not any more.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u662f\u554a\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\u6700\u8fd1\u5f00\u59cb\u51fa\u73b0\u4e86\u3002\u4ee5\u524d\u5979\u633a\u4f1a\u7ba1\u94b1\u7684\uff0c\u73b0\u5728\u5c31\u4e0d\u884c\u4e86\u3002","words_num":"21","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"15","start_time":"01:25.16","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"53.32","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"85.16"},{"id":"124227","content":"TOM: And be ready to tell them about anything you find particularly difficult about caring for your mother.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u53e6\u5916\uff0c\u4f60\u8981\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u628a\u7167\u987e\u8fc7\u7a0b\u4e2d\u9047\u5230\u7684\u5404\u79cd\u56f0\u96be\u544a\u8bc9\u4ed6\u4eec\u3002","words_num":"18","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"16","start_time":"02:18.48","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"5.80","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"138.48"},{"id":"124228","content":"CAROL: So recently I\u2019ve noticed she\u2019s started to have quite bad problems with her memory ... if I wasn\u2019t there, I think she\u2019d forget to eat, for example. And often she doesn\u2019t seem quite sure what day it is.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u6700\u8fd1\u6211\u6ce8\u610f\u5230\u5979\u7684\u8bb0\u5fc6\u529b\u660e\u663e\u53d8\u5dee\u4e86\u2026\u2026\u5982\u679c\u6211\u4e0d\u5728\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u5979\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u5fd8\u8bb0\u5403\u996d\u3002\u800c\u4e14\u5979\u5e38\u5e38\u641e\u4e0d\u6e05\u4eca\u5929\u661f\u671f\u51e0\u3002","words_num":"39","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"17","start_time":"02:24.28","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"14.56","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"144.28"},{"id":"124229","content":"TOM: Yes, tell them about that. And are there any physical difficulties you have caring for her? Lifting her, for example?","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u8fd9\u4e9b\u60c5\u51b5\u4e5f\u8981\u544a\u8bc9\u4ed6\u4eec\u3002\u4f60\u5728\u7167\u987e\u5979\u7684\u8fc7\u7a0b\u4e2d\uff0c\u6709\u6ca1\u6709\u9047\u5230\u4f53\u529b\u4e0a\u7684\u56f0\u96be\uff1f\u6bd4\u5982\u62b1\u5979\u6216\u8005\u642c\u52a8\u5979\u7684\u65f6\u5019\uff1f","words_num":"21","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"18","start_time":"02:38.84","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"7.88","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"158.84"},{"id":"124230","content":"CAROL: Yes. She\u2019s quite heavy, and I\u2019m afraid of hurting my back \u2013 I\u2019d be in real trouble if that happened.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u6709\u7684\u3002\u6211\u5988\u5f88\u91cd\uff0c\u6211\u62c5\u5fc3\u4f24\u5230\u8170\u2014\u2014\u8981\u662f\u4f24\u5230\u4e86\uff0c\u6211\u5c31\u5f7b\u5e95\u6ca1\u6cd5\u52a8\u5f39\u4e86\u3002","words_num":"21","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"19","start_time":"02:46.72","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"8.20","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"166.72"},{"id":"124231","content":"TOM: They can give you advice about that, and also about how to avoid the possibility of your mum having a fall.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u7ed9\u4f60\u4e00\u4e9b\u5efa\u8bae\uff0c\u6559\u4f60\u600e\u4e48\u907f\u514d\u5988\u5988\u6454\u5012\u7684\u98ce\u9669\u3002","words_num":"22","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"20","start_time":"02:54.92","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"5.96","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"174.92"},{"id":"124232","content":"CAROL: Great. So once they\u2019ve done this assessment, if I\u2019m eligible, what happens next?","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u592a\u597d\u4e86\u3002\u90a3\u7b49\u4ed6\u4eec\u505a\u5b8c\u8bc4\u4f30\u4ee5\u540e\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u6211\u80fd\u7b26\u5408\u6761\u4ef6\uff0c\u63a5\u4e0b\u6765\u4f1a\u6709\u4ec0\u4e48\u5b89\u6392\uff1f","words_num":"14","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"21","start_time":"03:00.88","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"7.88","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"180.88"},{"id":"124233","content":"TOM: Well, they might support you financially. So they might help you with transport costs, like if you have to get a taxi to take your mother for an appointment, for example.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u8003\u8651\u5bf9\u4f60\u63d0\u4f9b\u7ecf\u6d4e\u652f\u6301\u3002\u6bd4\u5982\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u8981\u6253\u8f66\u5e26\u5988\u5988\u53bb\u770b\u75c5\uff0c\u8fd9\u90e8\u5206\u4ea4\u901a\u8d39\u7528\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u5e2e\u4f60\u627f\u62c5\u3002","words_num":"32","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"22","start_time":"03:08.76","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"9.32","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"188.76"},{"id":"124234","content":"CAROL: I usually drive her myself actually. So could I claim for the petrol?","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u6211\u4e00\u822c\u81ea\u5df1\u5f00\u8f66\u9001\u5979\u3002\u90a3\u6211\u53ef\u4ee5\u62a5\u9500\u6c7d\u6cb9\u8d39\u5417\uff1f","words_num":"14","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"23","start_time":"03:18.08","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"5.68","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"198.08"},{"id":"124235","content":"TOM: You could, and you can claim for the insurance too.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u53ef\u4ee5\uff0c\u8fde\u8f66\u9669\u4e4b\u7c7b\u7684\u8d39\u7528\u4e5f\u53ef\u4ee5\u4e00\u8d77\u7533\u8bf7\u62a5\u9500\u3002","words_num":"11","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"24","start_time":"03:23.76","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"3.08","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"203.76"},{"id":"124236","content":"CAROL: Oh, right.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u54e6\uff0c\u660e\u767d\u4e86\u3002","words_num":"3","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"25","start_time":"03:26.84","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"1.28","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"206.84"},{"id":"124237","content":"TOM: And if you need help with the housework, they can arrange for someone to come along once or twice a week. And one other thing, I hope you don\u2019t mind me saying this, but it\u2019s important you look after yourself, and it seems to me you\u2019re under quite a bit of stress.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u9700\u8981\u5bb6\u653f\u670d\u52a1\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u8fd8\u53ef\u4ee5\u5b89\u6392\u6bcf\u5468\u4e00\u4e24\u6b21\u6709\u4eba\u6765\u6253\u626b\u6216\u505a\u996d\u3002\u987a\u4fbf\u8bf4\u4e00\u53e5\uff0c\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u4e0d\u4ecb\u610f\u6211\u8bf4\u8fd9\u4e2a\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u81ea\u5df1\u4e5f\u8981\u6ce8\u610f\u4f11\u606f\uff0c\u6211\u770b\u4f60\u73b0\u5728\u538b\u529b\u633a\u5927\u7684\u3002","words_num":"53","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"26","start_time":"03:28.12","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"14.12","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"208.12"},{"id":"124238","content":"CAROL: I am, yes.","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u662f\u7684\uff0c\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u786e\u5b9e\u633a\u7d2f\u7684\u3002","words_num":"4","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"27","start_time":"03:42.24","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"1.56","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"222.24"},{"id":"124239","content":"TOM: Well, tell the council, because they may be able to give you some advice on how to minimise it.","content_zh":"\u6c64\u59c6\uff1a\u90a3\u4f60\u4e00\u5b9a\u8981\u8ddf\u653f\u5e9c\u8bf4\u660e\u60c5\u51b5\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e5f\u4f1a\u7ed9\u4e00\u4e9b\u7f13\u89e3\u538b\u529b\u7684\u5efa\u8bae\u3002","words_num":"20","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"28","start_time":"03:43.80","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"5.48","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"223.80"},{"id":"124240","content":"CAROL: Really? Though actually I feel so much better having talked to you. I\u2019ll get in touch with the council straight away. Now shall we ...","content_zh":"\u5361\u7f57\u5c14\uff1a\u771f\u7684\u5417\uff1f\u4e0d\u8fc7\u8bf4\u5b9e\u8bdd\uff0c\u8ddf\u4f60\u804a\u5b8c\u6211\u611f\u89c9\u8f7b\u677e\u591a\u4e86\u3002\u6211\u6253\u7b97\u7acb\u523b\u8054\u7cfb\u6709\u5173\u90e8\u95e8\u3002\u90a3\u6211\u4eec\u73b0\u5728\u2026\u2026","words_num":"26","level":"2","parent":"124211","seq":"29","start_time":"03:49.28","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:56:32","updated_at":"2025-08-08 13:37:43","passport_id":"11877510","status":"0","collect_num":"0","audio_time":"14.72","audio_path":"","listen_num":"0","listen_people":"0","start_time_sec":"229.28"}],"start_time_sec":"1.20"}]}}},"relative_seq":["1","10"]}],"sectionSheet":{"id":956,"title":"C20T2S1","category_id":0,"type":0,"child_num":10,"subject":2,"question":[{"section_id":956,"qid":112905,"seq":1}],"quiz_configs":[]},"logs":[],"explains":{"112906":{"officialExplain":[]},"112907":{"officialExplain":{"id":"15485","question_id":"112907","audio_time":null,"explain":"<p>\u672c\u9898\u9700\u586b\u5165\u53ef\u6570\u540d\u8bcd\u5355\u6570\uff0c\u6839\u636e\u5217\u70b9\u5f0f\u5e76\u5217\u7ed3\u6784\u53ef\u77e5\uff0c\u672c\u9898\u548c\u9898\u5e72\u4e0a\u65b9\u7684time for other responsibilities\u4e3a\u5e76\u5217\u5173\u7cfb\u3002\u539f\u6587\u5728time for all the other responsibilities\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u51fa\u73b0\u5e76\u5217\u8fde\u63a5\u8bcdand also\uff0c\u968f\u540e\u51fa\u73b0\u7b54\u6848break\u3002<\/p>","subject":"24","praise_num":"0","step_num":"0","created_at":"2025-08-08 11:53:10","updated_at":"2025-08-08 11:53:10","type":"0","video_ids":"","teacher_id":"0"}},"112908":{"officialExplain":{"id":"15486","question_id":"112908","audio_time":null,"explain":"<p>\u6839\u636e\u9898\u5e72\u4e0a\u65b9\u5185\u5bb9\u53ef\u77e5\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u586b\u5165\u8ba8\u8bba\u7684\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u5185\u5bb9\u3002\u9898\u5e72\u4e2d\u7684how much\u63d0\u793a\u586b\u5165\u4e0d\u53ef\u6570\u540d\u8bcd\u3002\u7c97\u4f53\u5c0f\u6807\u9898Assessment of mother\u2019s needs\u539f\u8bcd\u91cd\u73b0\u3002\u4e0b\u4e00\u53e5\u4e2d\u7684talk to you about\u66ff\u6362\u9898\u5e72\u8bcddiscussion\u3002for a start\u63d0\u793a\u672c\u9898\u5373\u5c06\u51fa\u73b0\u3002the amount of\u540e\u63a5\u4e0d\u53ef\u6570\u